    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"making space\" sounds so exhausting. how am i supposed to grow anything when the foundation is just gone? it's like trying to build a house on top of a crater. it feels more like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life, waiting for the actual reality to catch up to the fact that i'm already empty. it's just... it's so heavy to carry this empty weight around every day.",
